data.description: REYNOLDSBURG Split Level - 4 bedroom on low traffic street. The very spacious backyard is ideal for pets, family BBQ's or simply a quiet summertime evening. Primary level has been updated with wood laminate & ceramic flooring in the kitchen. Newer appliances and a backyard view from the eat-in kitchen through the full view patio door. Upper level has original hardwood surfaces and updated full bath. The lower level has a plush feeling carpet in the spacious family room & bedroom. The oversized garage offers more than ample storage in addition to full size vehicle capacity.
